title: The Artie Quitter Podcast APR 05 2016 Tue.mp3
description:
After quitting the "Howard Stern Show," surviving a suicide attempt and hosting his own DirecTV program, comedian Artie Lange is venturing into a new frontier -- podcasting.

Joining Artie on this venture is long time friend & life partner Dan Falato.

Some Podcast regulars if Artie hasn't managed to burn that bridge include Comedians Joe Matarese, Geno Bisconte, Sue Costello, Chris Cotton, Stacey Prussman & Mike Bocchetti, which add to the vibe of hanging out with the guys -- talkin' sports and bustin' chops.


TODAY's SHOW  (01:21:48)

Episode 230.
Artie,Dan Falato & Bob Levy
